          "tz": 0
        },
        "subject": "LU-11673 testing: patch to test issue with patch",
        "message": "LU-11673 testing: patch to test issue with patch\n\nFor test only. \n\nInside the single bracket test function '[', the ‘-n’ flag\ndoes not work with unquoted arguments. The -n argument\nshould be quoted.\n\nQuote the ‘-n’ argument for Lustre test suite conf-sanity.sh\nand test-framework.sh.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly trivial\nTest-Parameters: testlist=replay-single\nTest-Parameters: envdefinitions=SLOW=\"no\",ONLY=\"27\" testlist=sanity\nTest-Parameters: envdefinitions=ONLY=\"27\" testlist=sanity\n\nSigned-off-by: James Nunez <jnunez@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ie9f85c4ccdab9170e29ba0bf087e30942866f384\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
